data.description: Looking for a beautiful home in Keystone of Galvez subdivision? This home offers an open floor plan with 3 bedrooms and 2 baths, wood floors in the living room, and a gas fireplace surrounded by granite. The kitchen features beautiful birch cabinets and stainless appliances. Also includes granite in the bathrooms, a separate shower and jetted tub in the primary bath, and a separate mud room with a computer nook. The backyard is fully fenced and offers an extended covered patio great for entertaining. X flood zone, and the home qualifies for 100% financing! New roof!
